# Delfinance API — REST Client (VS Code)
# Extensão necessária: REST Client (humao.rest-client)
#
# Preencha as variáveis abaixo com suas credenciais de Sandbox.
# Nunca commite valores reais — use um arquivo .env ou mantenha local.

@baseUrl    = https://apisandbox.delbank.com.br
@apiKey     = SUA_API_KEY_AQUI
@accountId  = SUA_ACCOUNT_ID_AQUI


# =============================================================================
# PIX — COBRANÇAS (CASH-IN)
# =============================================================================

### Criar cobrança Pix
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/pix/charges
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "amount": 150.75,
  "description": "Pagamento do pedido #9817",
  "customer": {
    "name": "Maria Oliveira",
    "document": "12345678909"
  }
}

###

### Consultar cobrança Pix
# @prompt chargeId ID da cobrança (ex: chg_981726a)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/pix/charges/chg_981726a
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### Consultar transação Pix
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/pix/transactions/pix_tx_123456
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}


# =============================================================================
# PIX — QR CODE ESTÁTICO
# =============================================================================

### Criar QR Code Estático
POST {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/static
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "correlationId": "2f908499-685c-4e36-af04-30567dc08dc5",
  "description": "QR Code reutilizável",
  "amount": 9.99,
  "additionalInformation": "Testando qrcode"
}

###

### Consultar QR Code Estático
# Substitua :transactionIdentifier pelo ID retornado na criação
GET {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/static/vchargeffeeed94cdbc41
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### Cancelar QR Code Estático
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/static/vchargeffeeed94cdbc41/cancel
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}


# =============================================================================
# PIX — QR CODE DINÂMICO
# =============================================================================

### Criar QR Code Dinâmico
POST {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/dynamic
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "correlationId": "40ede975-031d-4517-bdd4-31472d3f00a4",
  "amount": 99.90,
  "expiresIn": 1800,
  "formatResponse": "PAYLOAD_AND_QRCODE"
}

###

### Consultar QR Code Dinâmico
GET {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/dynamic/vchargeffab8b4c963344c283e491f5e
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### Cancelar QR Code Dinâmico
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/dynamic/vchargeffab8b4c963344c283e491f5e/cancel
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}


# =============================================================================
# PIX — QR CODE COM VENCIMENTO
# =============================================================================

### Criar QR Code com Vencimento
POST {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/due-date
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "correlationId": "ac7a235a-1a91-47b0-8da5-0eb75abf3617",
  "amount": 150.00,
  "dueDate": "2026-12-30",
  "formatResponse": "PAYLOAD_AND_QRCODE",
  "payer": {
    "name": "João Alves",
    "document": "07034346593"
  },
  "address": {
    "cityName": "ARACAJU",
    "zipCode": "49000000",
    "state": "SE",
    "street": "LOGRADOURO"
  },
  "taxes": {
    "interestType": "PERCENTAGE_PER_MONTH_CALENDAR_DAY",
    "interestAmount": 1,
    "fineType": "PERCENTAGE",
    "fineAmount": 2,
    "discountType": "FIXED_AMOUNT",
    "discountAmount": 10.00
  }
}

###

### Consultar QR Code com Vencimento
GET {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/due-date/wcharge0aac4378c3cf4c37b0ec16c7c
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### Cancelar QR Code com Vencimento
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/due-date/wcharge0aac4378c3cf4c37b0ec16c7c/cancel
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}


# =============================================================================
# PIX — TRANSFERÊNCIAS (CASH-OUT)
# =============================================================================

### 1. Inicializar pagamento por Chave Pix (obtém endToEndId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/dict/payment-initialization
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "key": "+5511999975734",
  "holderDocument": "30287697789"
}

###

### 2. Criar transferência Pix (use o endToEndId acima)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/pix/transfers
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "key": "financeiro@fornecedor.com",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "description": "Pagamento Fornecedor Lote #1"
}

###

### Consultar transferência Pix
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/pix/transfers/trsf_28173a
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### 1. Inicializar pagamento por QR Code (obtém endToEndId + transactionId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v2/pix/qrcode/payment-initialization
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "payload": "00020101021226820014br.gov.bcb.pix2560pix-h.delbank.com.br/v2/cob/vchargeffab8b4c963344c283e491f5e5204000053039865802BR5907DELBANK6007ARACAJU62070503***6304CB42"
}


# =============================================================================
# PIX — DEVOLUÇÕES
# =============================================================================

### Criar devolução Pix
# Substitua {endToEndIdOriginal} pelo endToEndId da transação recebida
PUT {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v1/transactions/pix/E182361202024041911111111111111/refund
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}
IdempotencyKey: {{$guid}}

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "externalId": "devolucao-pedido-9817",
  "description": "Devolução solicitada pelo cliente"
}

###

### Consultar devolução Pix
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/pix/refunds/ref_98127b
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}


# =============================================================================
# PIX — CHAVES PIX (DICT)
# =============================================================================

### Consultar chaves Pix da conta
GET {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v1/pix/dict/entries
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### Criar chave Pix (EVP — chave aleatória)
POST {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v1/pix/dict/entries
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}
IdempotencyKey: {{$guid}}

{
  "entryType": "EVP"
}

###

### Remover chave Pix
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v1/pix/dict/entries
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "key": "d882fe5b-0b8a-4b35-ac30-ed862bfa2222"
}


# =============================================================================
# BOLETO
# =============================================================================

### Criar boleto (BANKSLIP_PIX)
POST {{baseUrl}}/baas/v1/charges
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "type": "BANKSLIP_PIX",
  "correlationId": "{{$guid}}",
  "yourNumber": "PED-2024-001",
  "dueDate": "2026-12-30",
  "Amount": 150.00,
  "payer": {
    "name": "João Alves",
    "document": "07034346593",
    "email": "joao@email.com",
    "phone": { "prefix": "79", "number": "988669383" },
    "address": {
      "zipCode": "49010030",
      "publicPlace": "AV. RIO BRANCO",
      "neighborhood": "CENTRO",
      "number": "186",
      "city": "ARACAJU",
      "state": "SE"
    }
  }
}

###

### Consultar boleto
# Substitua o correlationId pelo GUID do boleto criado
GET {{baseUrl}}/baas/v1/charges/304c439c-4b17-4a75-abb1-2526e356cdad
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### Atualizar vencimento do boleto
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/baas/v1/charges/304c439c-4b17-4a75-abb1-2526e356cdad
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "dueDate": "2027-03-31"
}

###

### Cancelar boleto
PUT {{baseUrl}}/baas/v1/charges/304c439c-4b17-4a75-abb1-2526e356cdad/closeout
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### Imprimir boleto (retorna PDF — salvo via output)
# Nota: o REST Client salvará o binário; use "Save Response Body" no VS Code
GET {{baseUrl}}/baas/v1/charges/304c439c-4b17-4a75-abb1-2526e356cdad/stream
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### Simular pagamento de boleto (Sandbox)
# Use o barCode ou digitableLine retornados na criação como {id}
POST {{baseUrl}}/baas/v1/charges/43590001161200000060900002156347693070000000010/simulate-conclude
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{}


# =============================================================================
# WEBHOOKS
# =============================================================================

### Cadastrar webhook
POST {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v1/webhooks
Content-Type: application/json
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

{
  "eventType": "PIX_RECEIVED",
  "url": "https://seuservidor.com.br/webhooks/pix",
  "authorizationScheme": "BEARER",
  "authorization": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."
}

###

### Listar webhooks cadastrados
GET {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v1/webhooks
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}

###

### Remover webhook
# Substitua o ID pelo retornado no cadastro
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/baas/api/v1/webhooks/wbh_a1b2c3d4
x-delbank-api-key: {{apiKey}}
x-delfinance-account-id: {{accountId}}
